OL,3,CMan accused of dumping 27 tonnes of
OL,4,Cwaste will not face trial until March
OL,5,C2027
OL,7,FA man and the company of which he is a
OL,8,Fdirector has pleaded not guilty at
OL,9,FStafford Crown Court in connection
OL,10,Fwith the alleged dumping of 27 tonnes
OL,11,Fof waste on a Lichfield road.
OL,13,FDarren Sheen will not face trial until
OL,14,FMarch 2027 because of the court
OL,15,Fbacklog, a hearing today was told.
OL,17,FThe pile of waste, which was more than
OL,18,F20 metres in length, two metres in
OL,19,Fheight and weighed in excess of 27
OL,20,Ftonnes, blocked the lane restricting
OL,21,Faccess for residents and businesses.
