OL,13,Fwaste likely to cause pollution or
OL,14,Fharm to human health, driving a motor
OL,15,Fvehicle dangerously, failing without
OL,16,Freasonable excuse to record data on a
OL,17,Fdriver's card, wilful obstruction of a
OL,18,Fhighway, failure to take measures when
OL,19,Fmanaging extractive waste to prevent
OL,20,Fcontraventions and the escape of waste.
