OL,7,FThere are various punishments for
OL,8,Fflytipping including imprisonment,
OL,9,Funlimited fines as well as an order to
OL,10,Fdeprive rights to a vehicle used to
OL,11,Fcommit the offence.
OL,13,FLocal authorities usually deal with
OL,14,Fsmaller scale, more frequent incidents
OL,15,Fand the Environment Agency will deal
OL,16,Fwith larger scale, more serious
OL,17,Fincidents of illegal waste disposal.
